This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image reconstruction using deep learning. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as deep learning is a subset of these fields. The paper also mentions the use of natural image datasets, which suggests it may belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the analysis of patch sets suggests it may belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
